<td class="editor-text editor-text " align="left" valign="top" style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #403F42; text-align: left; display: block; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.2; padding: 10px 20px;"> 
                                 <div></div> 
                                 <div class="text-container galileo-ap-content-editor">
                                  <div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">Dear Students, Educators &amp; Parents/Guardians:</span>
                                   </div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <br>
</div> 
                                   <div> 
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">On behalf of the entire CSDNR leadership team, we hope you and your families are remaining safe and doing your best to follow guidance regarding measures to contain the spread of COVID-19 within our community. This global health crisis has taken us all by surprise and we are working quickly to respond. During this time, we all need to continue to support one another and work to stay informed, as information continues to shift rapidly. We remind you to please refer to the </span>
                                    <a href="https://www.nred.org/" target="_blank" style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: underline;">Coronavirus Resource Center</a>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;"> on the district's homepage for the latest updates on school closings, best practices for safety/containment, access to resources (food, childcare, etc), our planned Distance Learning Plan (formal launch tomorrow) and more.</span> 
                                   </div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <br>
</div> 
                                   <div> 
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">Events have unfolded quickly, and we recognize that this raises a range of important questions about potential impacts on students, families and our full community. We are already working to develop a list of </span>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</span>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"> </span>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">to provide answers to the questions that we have already encountered. This FAQ will soon be added to the district's Coronavirus Resource Center. To help us in this effort - and precisely because New Rochelle is among the first communities to confront this crisis - </span>
                                    <a href="https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/2ZWSV66" target="_blank" style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline;">we invite to you share your questions with us by clicking here</a>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">. </span> 
                                   </div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <br>
</div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">Where answers exist, we will work quickly to provide them. However, we anticipate that many others will require additional research and/or consultation with local, state or federal officials. In these cases, we will work to set clear expectations about how quickly (and the priority order in which) we are pursuing answers. In this time of uncertainty, we recognize that transparent access to more information is helpful for all of us.</span>
                                   </div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <br>
</div> 
                                   <div>
                                    <span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;">The CSDNR remains committed to leading through this crisis with open and transparent communications and innovative solutions to support the continued imperative of teaching and learning. We are focused on the instructional initiative, the CSNDR “Distance Learning Plan” being launched tomorrow. Our priority is the safety and education of all our students. Hearing from you will help us identify areas we may be able to more effectively communicate.</span>
                                   </div> 
